text: Szymanek is a Polish surname. It is a patronymic surname derived from the given name Szymon. "Skąd pochodzą nazwiska?", Histmag, May 16, 2006 .Notable people with the surname include: *Nik Szymanek, British amateur astronomer and astrophotographer *Wojciech Szymanek (born 1982), Polish footballer *Jolanta Szymanek-Deresz (1954–2010), Polish politician ==References== Category:Polish- language surnames Category:Patronymic surnames
